{"tid":110383,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"今日同個大陸親戚去食壽司","createTime":"2017-02-06T15:35:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-16T14:58:56.000Z","uid":11805,"like":87,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3a64cd71f7e1a93e49b1a8c20e7695bc35262708","tid":110383,"uid":11805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T15:35:57.000Z","msg":"話說新年咁就有個廣西既親戚來左香港玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就老母既表弟,即係表舅父la<br />\n咁岩今日放假,老母就叫我帶呀表舅父出去玩下<br />\n咁我就帶左佢去元氣食壽司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一坐底睇下menu<br />\n佢:軍艦是啥意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我:拾磨?<br />\n佢:軍艦呀!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(原來即係有舊紫菜包住嗰啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n但我普通話好屎,就求其解釋la<br />\n我:就是船<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢:船<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我:對對對<br />\n佢:(好似恍然大悟咁)就是在海船上捉的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我:(心諗so9sad) 對對對!<br />\n<br />\n過左一陣<br />\n佢:為啥會有炸雞軍艦?海裡有雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我:(忍笑)對對對,香港d海有g也<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢:操,那麼妙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n又過左一陣<br />\n佢:香港的海還有玉米呢!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我:(已經諗唔到解釋)對對對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後費事再煩拿拿聲食完埋單<br />\n大陸親戚真係好難應付<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8d26d5cd4fec7c338453adf2b90da2f9180abe8","tid":110383,"uid":36829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r